{"tid":534789,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"四萬中國品牌萬普拉斯客戶信用卡資料外洩","createTime":"2018-01-20T07:34:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-25T06:41:41.000Z","uid":55951,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ed6585eb81aa5c7277c39438cb40cdd5b421692e","tid":534789,"uid":55951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T07:34:46.000Z","msg":"日前我們報導過有 OnePlus 用戶投訴，在過去 2 個月曾經在官網購物，之後信用卡被盜用，懷疑 OnePlus 外洩他們的信用卡資料。結果今天 OnePlus 終於承認並在官方討論區發聲明，表示由於出現保安漏洞，多達 4 萬名顧客的資料受到影響。<br />\n<br />\nOnePlus 表示惡意程式碼加入到官網的付款程式，在去年 11 月中至今年 1 月 11 日期間，於用戶輸入時竊取他們的信用卡或銀行卡資料，現時該程式碼已經被移除。OnePlus 指 3 類顧客：使用預先儲存的信用卡支付、透過 PayPal 以信用卡支付、直接透過 PayPal 帳號支付，應該不會受到影響。<br />\n<br />\nOnePlus 表示已經聯絡受影響的顧客，又會和交易服務供應商合作，確保同樣事情未來不會再發生。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/01/20/40k-oneplus-customer-credit-card-info-leaked/tech-secure/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F01%2F20%2F40k-oneplus-customer-credit-card-info-leaked%2Ftech-secure%2F&d=Gp8aH3skem65Oem7sUL1du9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=39bc9311\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/01/20/40k-oneplus-customer-credit-card-info-leaked/tech-secure/</a><br />\n<br />\n中伏嘅受害人cut咗卡未？"},{"pid":"45d85270a928c29286a68bf2a2d61d127b5e66f4","tid":534789,"uid":13663,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T07:38:30.000Z","msg":"性價比好高<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (唔計畀人偷card)"},{"pid":"43f9494a7b539b5f501ec100510b75732c12244d","tid":534789,"uid":55951,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T07:41:42.000Z","msg":"班鬼佬真係多嘢睇<br />\n而家可以睇埋信用卡資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff1c4dbf1b7d6f22ae32c45e2c08558f19d1d886","tid":534789,"uid":60179,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T08:35:49.000Z","msg":"可以cut多幾多次?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2677a2c9d84de3b0b8a7ec9605229c1b8500a290","tid":534789,"ui